<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Welcome</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f0f0f0;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    .header {
      background-color: #ffffff;
    }

    .logo {
      width: 60px;
      height: auto;
      display: block;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .greeting {
      margin-top: 20px;
      font-weight: bold;
      text-align: left;
      color: #145A32;
    }

    .message {
      margin-top: 20px;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .cta-button {
      display: block;
      margin: 30px 0;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 15px 0;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border: 2px solid #145A32;
      color: #145A32;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }

    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      background-color: #145A32;
      color: #ffffff;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .footer a {
      color: #ffffff;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <img class="logo" src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dpmx02shl/image/upload/v1741383995/logo_rujohq.png" alt="Logo" />
      <h4 class="greeting">Dear Investor <%= name %>,</h4>
    </div>
    <div class="message">
      <p>We wanted to send a quick note to express our sincere gratitude for referring <%= amount %> to Fortune Holders Associate!</p>
      <p>
        We're thrilled they've joined our community and started using website, and we know they'll find valuable resources and tools they need to succeed.
        Your support means the world to us and helps us grow. We really appreciate you spreading the word!
      </p>
      <p>
        If you have any questions or need assistance, please don't hesitate to
        contact us. We are always happy to help. Best regards
      </p>
    </div>
    <a class="cta-button" href="https://www.fortuneholders.com/user/dashboard">Access Your Dashboard</a>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; <%= year %>. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p>
        For inquiries, please contact our support center at
        <a href="mailto:support@fortuneholders.com">support@fortuneholders.com</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>

</html>